data.description: Welcome to this inviting 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home nestled in the charming Whitehall community. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of hardwood floors that seamlessly flow throughout the first floor.The open floor plan of this residence is tailor-made for effortless entertaining, providing ample space for hosting large family gatherings and creating lasting memories. The kitchen, a focal point of this home, boasts elegant granite countertops, abundant cabinetry, a convenient island, and a spacious pantry, making it a chef's delight.Venturing to the second floor via the staircase, you'll discover the luxurious owner's suite. Accentuated by vaulted ceilings, this retreat features walk-in closets and an en-suite bathroom equipped with a generous soaking tub,offering a perfect escape for relaxation.  This property is equipped with modern amenities and updates, ensuring comfort and convenience. The HVAC system has been thoughtfully upgraded, with a new unit installed upstairs and a new fan motor and compressor for the downstairs unit. A brand-new water heater, garbage disposer, and dishwasher add a touch of contemporary functionality to the home. The garage door opener is also new, ensuring seamless access to your abode.  Other notable features include a six-year-old roof, providing both durability and peace of mind.   Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home, where modern amenities blend seamlessly with timeless charm. Welcome to a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication in the heart of the Whitehall community.
